pub enum ScryptoCustomValueKind {

Show 16 variants    PackageAddress,
    ComponentAddress,
    ResourceAddress,
    Own,

    Proof,
    Expression,
    Blob,
    Hash,
    EcdsaSecp256k1PublicKey,
    EcdsaSecp256k1Signature,
    EddsaEd25519PublicKey,
    EddsaEd25519Signature,
    Decimal,
    PreciseDecimal,
    NonFungibleLocalId,

}
